cu.explanation_en: Setting the NGU IP address to the same as the AMF IP (192.168.70.132) creates an IP conflict, preventing proper network interface binding and causing connection failures.

du.explanation_en: Setting T1a_cp_ul timing parameter to 0 causes timing misalignment, leading to synchronization issues and potential frame transmission failures in the DU.
du.explanation_zh: 將 T1a_cp_ul 定時參數設定為 0 會導致定時錯位，造成 DU 中的同步問題和潛在的幀傳輸失敗。
